data.description: Welcome to Florida living within the serene confines of Hernando Oaks, an exclusive golf course enclave secured by a gated entry. This meticulously designed 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence beckons with its versatile den/office, a space poised to effortlessly transition between functionality and sophistication. Upon entry, a world of comfort unfolds, seamlessly blending style with practicality through an open floor plan that bathes the living space with natural light. The kitchen, an epicureans's delight, showcases an island, granite countertops, modern appliances, and an abundant amount of storage. The master suite is a heaven of tranquility, boasting a spacious bedroom ensuite bathroom adorned with every desirable amenity, enhanced by an expansive walk-in closet. The additional bedrooms exude versatility. Living in Hernando Oaks not only grants the privileges of a gated community, but also ensures security and exclusivity. Nestled near vibrant shopping, dining and entertainment options, this home harmoniously combines tranquility and accessibility. Seize this unparalleled opportunity to embrace a lifestyle where every detail is meticulously tailored for your utmost enjoyment.
